         <OBJECT_CONTRACT>
            <TITLE>
               <P>Framework Agreement for Repair and Maintenance of Public Rights of Ways, Parks and Play Areas</P>
            </TITLE>
            <REFERENCE_NUMBER>Proc-17-20</REFERENCE_NUMBER>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="77313000"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SERVICES"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>Wrexham County Borough Council (WCBC) is looking to establish a framework agreement to carry out maintenance work on Public Rights of Way, Parks and Play Areas. The framework will be split into the following lots:</P>
               <P>Lot 1 – Public Rights of Way Works.</P>
               <P>Lot 2 – Parks and Play Area Works.</P>
               <P>It is anticipated that no more than 3 contractors will be appointed to Lot 1 and no more than 4 contractors will be appointed to Lot 2. Contractors can bid for and be successful on one or both lots.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <VAL_TOTAL CURRENCY="GBP">40000</VAL_TOTAL>
            <NO_LOT_DIVISION/>
            <OBJECT_DESCR ITEM="1">
               <CPV_ADDITIONAL>
                  <CPV_CODE CODE="77313000"/>
               </CPV_ADDITIONAL>
               <CPV_ADDITIONAL>
                  <CPV_CODE CODE="34928200"/>
